  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text govuk-heading-l">
    Devolution of powers to Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
      <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Explaining the background to devolution and how the legislatures and administrations of Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland work.</p>

  </div>
</div>

